{"id": 5058, "title": "Ticket #5058: kbdd does not work with shared port daemon", "description": "<blockquote>\nThe kbdd uses UDP to contact the startd.  This means the kbdd stops working if you turn on the shared port deamon (which causes daemons to stop listening on UDP).\n\n<p>Correct this problem by using a TCP connection from the kbdd to the startd.  For efficiency, the connection should persist.</p></blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\n<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"tktview?tn=5239\" title=\"Backport shared port / keyboard daemon fix to 8.2.10\">#5239</a></span></td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"center\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon ptr1\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\nBackport shared port / keyboard daemon fix to 8.2.10</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>", "attachments": "", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2015-Aug-26 13:11</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"chngview?cn=45725\">[45725]</a></span>: (<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"tktview?tn=5058\" title=\"kbdd does not work with shared port daemon\">#5058</a></span>) Convert kbdd from using UDP to using a persistent TCP connection.  (By Todd L Miller )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2015-Jul-13 15:22</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"chngview?cn=45291\">[45291]</a></span>: (<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"tktview?tn=5058\" title=\"kbdd does not work with shared port daemon\">#5058</a></span>) Version history item.  (By Todd L Miller )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2015-Jul-13 15:21</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"chngview?cn=45290\">[45290]</a></span>: (<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"tktview?tn=5058\" title=\"kbdd does not work with shared port daemon\">#5058</a></span>) Version history item.  (By Todd L Miller )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2015-May-19 09:32</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"chngview?cn=44872\">[44872]</a></span>: (<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"tktview?tn=5058\" title=\"kbdd does not work with shared port daemon\">#5058</a></span>) Convert kbdd from using UDP to using a persistent TCP connection.  (By Todd L Miller )</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>", "type": "enhance", "last_change": "2015-Jul-13 16:44", "status": "resolved", "created": "2015-May-19 09:31", "fixed_version": "2015-May-19 09:31", "broken_version": "", "priority": "4", "subsystem": "DaemonsExecNode", "assigned_to": "tlmiller", "derived_from": "#3813", "creator": "tlmiller", "rust": "", "customer_group": "other", "visibility": "public", "notify": "tlmiller@cs.wisc.edu", "due_date": ""}